{"questionId":"13295","questionHtml":"<p>Let <em><strong>a</strong></em>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  2 \\\\   k \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>k</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and <em><strong>b</strong></em> = <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  { - 3} \\\\   {k + 2} \\\\   k  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>k</mi>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>k</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>, <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k \\in \\mathbb{R}\">\n  <mi>k</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">R</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p>\n<p>Given that <em><strong>a</strong></em> and <em><strong>b</strong></em> are perpendicular, find the possible values of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k\">\n  <mi>k</mi>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p style=\"color:#999;font-size:90%;font-style:italic;\">* This question is from an exam for a previous syllabus, and may contain minor differences in marking or structure.</p><p><em><strong>a </strong></em>•<em><strong> </strong></em><em><strong>b</strong></em>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  2 \\\\   k \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right) \\bullet \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  { - 3} \\\\   {k + 2} \\\\   k  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>k</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>∙</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>k</mi>\n              <mo>+</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>k</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" =&nbsp; - 6 + k\\left( {k + 2} \\right) - k\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>k</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mi>k</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>a </strong></em>•<em><strong> </strong></em><em><strong>b</strong></em>&nbsp;= 0&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{k^2} + k - 6 = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>k</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>attempt at solving their quadratic equation&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {k + 3} \\right)\\left( {k - 2} \\right) = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k =&nbsp; - 3{\\text{,}}\\,\\,2\">\n  <mi>k</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Attempt at solving using |<em><strong>a</strong></em>||<em><strong>b</strong></em>|&nbsp;= |<em><strong>a</strong></em> × <em><strong>b</strong></em>| will be <em><strong>M1A0A0A0</strong></em> if neither answer found <em><strong>M1(A1)A1A0</strong></em><br>for one correct answer and <strong><em>M1(A1)A1A1</em></strong> for two correct answers.</p>\n<p><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p